## What Works

- Fixing the `search_apis` → `search_api_docs` typo was critical — the agent couldn't discover APIs without this
- Structured workflow in prompt (get passwords → search APIs → login → call APIs → complete) helps agent follow correct sequence
- Simple Spotify query tasks (most-liked song, least-played song, most-played in album library) pass reliably

## What Doesn't Work

- Vague API guidance ("search for review APIs") doesn't help mutation tasks — agent needs exact parameter names and workflow steps
- Adding API name hints without exact signatures doesn't improve mutation success
- Venmo guidance with assumed API signatures didn't help — the `show_contacts()` API may not provide Venmo user IDs directly, or relationship field names may differ from task wording

